呼んでみても 五千年の
Even if you call, a five-thousand-year...

524
00:30:53,196 --> 00:30:59,996
夢を今も 見続けてる
...dream, he's still seeing today.

525
00:31:01,196 --> 00:31:04,496
タイムトラベルは 楽し
Traveling in time is fun

